{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/course/dm/note/1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"mem 的小站"}},"post":{"id":"25cb9085-132a-5ad5-814a-4ae9bb394663","excerpt":"1. Propositional Logic 1.1. Propositions 命题(proposition)：A declarative sentence that is either  or , but not both. 悖论(paradox) 不属于命题（e.g. This statement is…","html":"<h2 id=\"1-Propositional-Logic\" style=\"position:relative;\">1. Propositional Logic<a href=\"#1-Propositional-Logic\" aria-label=\"1 Propositional Logic permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-Propositions\" style=\"position:relative;\">1.1. Propositions<a href=\"#11-Propositions\" aria-label=\"11 Propositions permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>命题(proposition)</strong>：A <strong>declarative sentence</strong> that is either <code class=\"language-text\">true</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>, but not both.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>悖论(paradox)</strong> 不属于命题（e.g. <em>This statement is false.</em> or <em>I'm lying.</em>）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>命题逻辑(propositional logic)</strong>：The area of logic that deals with propositions.</p>\n<p><strong>命题变量(propositional variable)</strong>: Small letters such as <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>q</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>r</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>s</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mo>…</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p,q,r,s,\\ldots</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\">…</span></span></span></span></span> used to present propositions.</p>\n<h3 id=\"12-Logic-Connectives\" style=\"position:relative;\">1.2. Logic Connectives<a href=\"#12-Logic-Connectives\" aria-label=\"12 Logic Connectives permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>逻辑连接词(logic connectives = logic operators)</strong>：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Connectives</th>\n<th>Expression</th>\n<th>Note</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Negation (NOT)</td>\n<td><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">¬</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lnot p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">¬</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Conjunction (AND)</td>\n<td><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>∧</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p \\land q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.75em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">∧</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Disjunction (OR)</td>\n<td><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>∨</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p\\lor q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.75em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">∨</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Exclusive Or (XOR)</td>\n<td><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>⊕</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p\\oplus q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⊕</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Implication</td>\n<td><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p\\rightarrow q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></td>\n<td>参见下节</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>英语中的单词 or 既可以表示 inclusive or 也可以表示 exclusive or（e.g. <em>George was born in 1956 or 1957.</em>）</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"121-Implication\" style=\"position:relative;\">1.2.1. Implication<a href=\"#121-Implication\" aria-label=\"121 Implication permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><strong>推断(implication) or 条件语句(conditional statement)</strong>：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p\\rightarrow q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span>, false when <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span></span> is true and <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span> is false.</p>\n<p><strong>假设(hypothesis = antecedent = premise)</strong>：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><strong>结论(conclusion = consequence)</strong>: <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>From <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p\\rightarrow q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span> we can form new conditional statements:</p>\n<p><strong>否命题(converse)</strong>：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>q</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q\\rightarrow p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><strong>逆命题(inverse)</strong>：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">¬</mi><mi>p</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">¬</mi><mi>q</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lnot p\\rightarrow \\lnot q</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">¬</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">¬</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><strong>逆否命题(contrapositive)</strong>：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">¬</mi><mi>q</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">¬</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lnot q\\rightarrow \\lnot p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">¬</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">¬</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><details open disabled class=\"callout callout-type-important\"><summary>逆否命题与原命题等价</summary><div><p></p><p>The contrapositive has <strong>the same truth values</strong> as the original implication.</p></div></details></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-谓词逻辑\" style=\"position:relative;\">2. 谓词逻辑<a href=\"#2-%E8%B0%93%E8%AF%8D%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91\" aria-label=\"2 谓词逻辑 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"3-Proof\" style=\"position:relative;\">3. Proof<a href=\"#3-Proof\" aria-label=\"3 Proof permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-propositional-logic\">1. Propositional Logic</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#11-propositions\">1.1. Propositions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#12-logic-connectives\">1.2. Logic Connectives</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-%E8%B0%93%E8%AF%8D%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91\">2. 谓词逻辑</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#3-proof\">3. Proof</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"I Logic & Proofs","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/course/dm/note/1/","isDoc":true,"category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"25cb9085-132a-5ad5-814a-4ae9bb394663","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":"[{\"slug\":\"/course/dm\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/dm/index.md\",\"title\":\"课程简介\"},{\"title\":\"笔记\",\"children\":[{\"slug\":\"/course/dm/note/1\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/dm/note/1.md\",\"title\":\"I Logic & Proofs\"}]}]"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}